TRAINING CLASS 8:
1.	Write a program to check whether the number is divisible by 2 and 3 and both (take prompt)
 <script>
        let a=parseInt(prompt("enter number"))
        if(a%2==0 && a%3==0){
            alert("divisble by both")
        }
        else if(a%2==0){
            alert("divisible by 2")
        }
        else if(a%3==0){
            alert("divisible by 3")
        }
        else{
            alert("not divisible")
        }   
 </script>

2.	Write a program to find the largest number out of three numbers expected from the user
let a=parseInt(prompt("enter first number"))
        let b=parseInt(prompt("enter second number"))
        let c=parseInt(prompt("enter third number"))
        if(a>b && a>c){
            alert("a is the largest")
        }
        else if(b>a && b>c){
            alert("b is the largest")
        }
        else{
            alert("c is the largest")
        }

3.	Accept the following from the user and calculate the percentage of classes attended:
a)	Total number of working days
b)	Total number of days for absent
          After calculating percentage show that, if the percentage is less than 75, then student will not be eligible to write exam.
let a=parseInt(prompt("enter number of working days"))
        let b=parseInt(prompt("enter number of days for absent"))
        percentage=((a-b)/a)*100
        if(percentage>=75){
            alert("student is eligible to write exam")
        }
        else{
            alert("student is not eligible to write exam")
        }

4.	A company decided to give bonus to employee according to the following criteria:
Time period of Service     bonus
	More than 10 years               10%
          >=6 and <=10		    8%
	Less than 6 years                  5%
Ask the user for their salary and years of service and print the bonus amount
 let salary= parseInt(prompt("enter salary"))
        let years=parseInt(prompt("enter years of service"))
        if(years>10){
            bonus=(salary*10)/100
            alert("bonus is "+bonus)
            totalsalary=salary+bonus
            document.write("total salary is "+totalsalary)

        }
        else if(years>=6 && years<=10){
            bonus=(salary*8)/100
            alert("bonus is "+bonus)
            totalsalary=salary+bonus
            document.write("total salary is "+totalsalary)

        }
        else if(years<6){
            bonus=(salary*5)/100
            alert("bonus is "+bonus)
            totalsalary=salary+bonus
            document.write("total salary is "+totalsalary)
        }
        else{
            alert("no bonus")
        }

